                      "text": "主线章节预告PV-「足迹」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/27/59155606/03c9ce4918b820efd177bd5f9938b6ba_6547060795176016543.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2020年9月28日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "【Prologue.捕风的异乡人】-【I.辞行久远之躯】-【II.千手百眼天下人间】",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "【III.虚空劫灰往世书】-【IV.罪人舞步旋】-【V.炽烈的还魂诗】-【VI.无神怜爱的雪国】",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube(JP):",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "《原神 · 提瓦特篇》主线章节预告PV-「足迹」：",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "https://ys.mihoyo.com/main/news/detail/116275",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "4.7版本PV：「纺坠终久之梦」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/26/59155606/9b42d35f9a503427ac6a0d50d08badc2_5830659153579213947.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2024年5月24日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "人们常困于过去的事情。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "那些无法弥补的遗憾，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "那些没能收到回应的疑问，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "或许会在未来得以圆满，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "又或许只能在梦中反复重映。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "动画短片—「未行之路」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/26/59155606/6761bae9b3f1a9984dc80837e9c4f0db_8521838436493768305.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2024年5月24日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "…可是，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "至少你依然还在世界的某处。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "曾经划过天空的流星尾迹，",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "便是如今我追寻你的未行之路。",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
